What I did is to install the available libraries from the page. Then, enter the folder:
C:\Program Files (x86)\National Instruments\LabVIEW 2020\vi.lib\Rock Robotics\WPI\ThirdParty\sensors
Copy the navX folder into the 2023 folder (same path). Reboot Labview, and you can find the libraries, directly under WPI Robotics Library --> Sensors --> Third Party you will find the NavX VI’s. They work out of the box.

I hope this helps.
